<subSubSection pageId="129" pageNumber="700" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="129.[2091,2677,705,1128]" pageId="129" pageNumber="700">
Previously classified as a subspecies of N. goral. The generic name was originally spelled 
<taxonomicName box="[2218,2389,859,892]" class="Mammalia" family="Bovidae" genus="Naemorhedus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="129" pageNumber="700" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Naemorhedus</taxonomicName>
, but the spelling 
<taxonomicName box="[2092,2263,898,931]" class="Mammalia" family="Bovidae" genus="Nemorhaedus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="129" pageNumber="700" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Nemorhaedus</taxonomicName>
, despite being an unjustified emendation, is “in prevailing” usage and is used here. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
